title: Breaking Bad Season 1 (1080p x265 Joy)
description:
Breaking Bad Season 1 Complete, in 1080p in H265 aka HEVC and AAC 5.1 audio all for about 378mb each!
Encoded using 2 pass, from the Bluray, with the slow setting for the highest quality possible.
The first season Bluray is very grainy, the loss in quality can not be helped. 

image

Any questions, or help playing this file, click on the HEVC banner just above. 
Please watch before rating or commenting on quality. Thank you KickAss community!
